quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Pellet, jippin…óo Alqur'aana on e maa…óa, ko duttoo-wo ma ka woowaandi maa. Maaku: "Ko Joomi am …ďuri anndude ardu…óo e peewal, e gon…óo e majjere …ďanngunde"."
  28,86,"A wonaano tam∆īininoo…óo jippineede deftere nden e maa…óa. Si wonaa tun, ko yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa. Wota won muk, balloowo heefer…ďe …ďen."
  28,87,"wota …ďe palo ma kadi e aayeeje Alla …óen, …ďaawo …óe jippineede e maa…óa. Noddu (yim…ďe …ďen) fa'ade e Joomi maa, wota a won muk, jiyaa…óo e sirkoo…ďe …ďen."
  28,88,"Wota a rewudu e Alla, dewetee…óo goo. Dewetee…óo goo alaa, si wonaa KaŇčko. Hu'unde fof re'ay, si wonaa Jaati Maako Kin. Ko KaŇčko woodani √Īaawugol; ko ka Makko kadi ndttete…óon."
  29,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  29,2,"E yim…ďe …ďen cikku …ďe ngaccirte nii, fii …ďe wi'ii: "Min ngooŇč…óinii!" Hara …ďe pitninaaka?"
  29,3,"GooŇč…óii, Min pitninii …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe. Maa Alla fe√Ī√Īin, fii gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, maa O fe√Ī√Īin kadi, fii fenoo…ďe …ďen."
  29,4,"Kaa gollu…ďe bon…ói …ďen cikku, won'nde …ďe laawoto Min? ko …ďe √Īaawata kon bonii!"
  29,5,"Kala taw…óo homo njortii kawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ngandu…óo on."
  29,6,"Kala kadi tii…ónii…óo, ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko jon'dinii…óo e tageefo ngon."